$ Excel: Ribbon Bar

The *Ribbon Bar* displays one → Microsoft/Office/Excel/GUI/Ribbon/tabs[tab] at a time.

{ Ribbon Display Options

  The *Ribbon Display Options* are found in the top right corner of → Microsoft/Office/Excel:
  gh|about-Excel|/GUI/Ribbon/img/Ribbon-Display-Options.png||

  Alternatively, the Ribbon can also be shown or hidden with the `ctrl+F1` → Microsoft/Office/Excel#excel-key-shortcut[keyboard shortcut].

}
{ Hiding/showing Ribbon Bar with Visual Basic for Applications #xls-show-hide-ribbon-vba

  In → development/languages/VBA, the Ribbon Bar can be shown or hidden like so:
code {
→ Microsoft/Office/Excel/Object-Model/Application#excel-application-executeExcel4Macro[application.executeExcel4Macro] "show.toolbar(""ribbon"", true )"
→ Microsoft/Office/Excel/Object-Model/Application#excel-application-executeExcel4Macro[application.executeExcel4Macro] "show.toolbar(""ribbon"", false)"
code }

}
